{"tid":245343,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"求意見 想入去平面設計","createTime":"2017-05-16T07:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T13:02:42.000Z","uid":13978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2972e9acee413599fcac7bf5c07c1f45aebc514b","tid":245343,"uid":13978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T07:28:21.000Z","msg":"Hd design 邊科唔講會自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身識識地ps ai indesign  cad<br />\n夠交功課但唔太熟<br />\n<br />\n相信好多巴打會叫我自學 仲快仲大自由度<br />\n但係我去見工需要張證書<br />\n雖然我以前有一堆design功課<br />\n但本身唔係平面設計出身 應該唔會理我<br />\n<br />\n想問下邊到可以上ps ai 課程 幫到我見工入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda8a69b50d96ca2d377bda5881da60f83c41d11","tid":245343,"uid":13978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T07:30:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.formwelkin.com/ps-ai/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.formwelkin.com%2Fps-ai%2F&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=ac6b93c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.formwelkin.com/ps-ai/</a><br />\n上網見到呢類 有資助又有adobe證書<br />\n係咪比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667c80b0afdb10fe99175df5d57da446902acdb3","tid":245343,"uid":13978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T07:32:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.formwelkin.com/ps-ai/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.formwelkin.com%2Fps-ai%2F&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=ac6b93c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.formwelkin.com/ps-ai/</a><br />\n上網見到呢類 有資助又有adobe證書<br />\n係咪比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class